originalText.text: Working with Anna has empowered me to completely change my life. Anna is a fantastic person and an excellent coach. When I started working with her I was living my life in fear and I was full of limiting beliefs. With her coaching and direct approach my perspective completely shifted. Before working with Anna I believed that I had very limited options for my future, I could not even begin to imagine all of the possibilites. Now I have started my own business that I am SO passionate about and I am living a life that I truly love. I can't recommend Anna enough. She will rock your world.

originalText.text: I only have wonderful things to say about my experience with Anna. From our first meeting through the end of my coaching experience with her, Anna was an excellent listener, extremely insightful and intuitive and always was 100% spot on in asking all the right questions to really help you dig deeply within yourself - where all the answers already lie! After each session I felt like a huge weight had been lifted off my shoulders, and I believed that Anna helped me harness my confidence to answer some tough questions and make some important decisions. She helped me in all facets of my life from career to family to relationships, and in the couple months we worked together a lot of positive things started to change and happen for me. While I know I was responsible for that change, I can say with complete confidence that Anna was the catalyst to help me through it. I would recommend her to anyone I know - whether you have a small challenge to tackle or something much greater. I cannot be more grateful for Anna's coaching and the positive changes I saw in my life as a result of our sessions.

originalText.text: In working with Anna, I've gotten to know myself in ways I never knew existed.  I don't have all the answers, but with her help and guidance, things became clearer to me.  She's transformative, inspiring, tough, but understanding.  Anna's dedication to helping me understand my patterns, transform my habits and self respect has boosted my confidence immensely.  I am a better person because of her, and now have the tools to continue on the path of betterment.

originalText.text: Working with Anna has had a tremendous impact on my life. She’s an amazing and dedicated life coach. Anna helped me to learn how to step back and observe circumstances and situations from different angles. We also worked on problem solving techniques that I’ve continued to implement months after our sessions. Whether by phone or email, she was accessible and available to help me with smaller issues that arose throughout the workweek. Overall, Anna has helped me develop skills that I’ll be able to use long after coaching and she’s just darn good at what she does.

originalText.text: Anna makes me feel like I'm the smartest, most creative person in the whole world. She makes me feel so special and it's because her gift is to be able to instantly see my talents. Anna encourages me to live big and to follow my dreams, she is my biggest cheerleader, and I have become significantly more positive and hopeful that I will be successful because of her enthusiasm of my talents. I would pay whatever the price to work with Anna because the results I gained from our experience together- in my body, mind, and spirit- are invaluable to me. Thank you, Anna! #goteamLA
